"Your Cutling keyboard is ready! While typing anywhere, tap the 🌐 globe icon on your keyboard to switch to Cutling." = "Vaša Cutling tipkovnica je pripravljena! Med tipkanjem kjerkoli tapnite ikono 🌐 globusa na tipkovnici, da preklopite na Cutling.";
"Follow the two simple steps below to start using your custom keyboard. This page will automatically update as you complete each step." = "Sledite dvema preprostima korakoma spodaj, da začnete uporabljati svojo prilagojeno tipkovnico. Ta stran se bo samodejno posodobila, ko dokončate vsak korak.";
"**Step 1:** Tap 'Open Cutling Settings' below, go to **Keyboards** and select **Cutling** from the list." = "**Korak 1:** Tapnite „Odpri Cutling nastavitve“ spodaj, pojdite na **Tipkovnice** in izberite **Cutling** s seznama.";
"**Step 2:** Make sure **Allow Full Access** is ON. This lets the keyboard copy images to your clipboard. Your data stays private and is never sent anywhere." = "**Korak 2:** Prepričajte se, da je **Dovoli polni dostop** vklopljeno. To omogoča tipkovnici kopiranje slik v vaše odložišče. Vaši podatki ostanejo zasebni in se nikoli ne pošljejo nikamor.";
"**Step 3:** Tap on the text input and choose \"Cutling\" using the 🌐 globe icon on your keyboard to update the \"Full Access\" status." = "**Korak 3:** Tapnite besedilno polje za vnos in izberite „Cutling“ z ikono 🌐 globusa na tipkovnici, da posodobite stanje „Polni dostop“.";
"**Step 4:** You're good to go! The usage guide is provided below." = "**Korak 4:** Pripravljeni ste! Navodila za uporabo so spodaj.";
"While typing in any app, tap or hold the 🌐 globe key at the bottom-left of your keyboard, then select Cutling" = "Med tipkanjem v kateri koli aplikaciji tapnite ali pridržite tipko 🌐 globusa spodaj levo na tipkovnici, nato izberite Cutling";
"Tap any text cutling and it will be typed into your current text field immediately" = "Tapnite kateri koli besedilni cutling in takoj bo vtipkan v vaše trenutno besedilno polje";
"Tap an image cutling to copy it to your clipboard, then paste it into the app you're using (usually by tapping and holding, then selecting Paste). Apple currently does not support directly pasting an image on this app." = "Tapnite slikovni cutling, da ga kopirate v odložišče, nato ga prilepite v aplikacijo, ki jo uporabljate (običajno s tapom in pridržanjem, nato izberite Prilepi). Apple trenutno ne podpira neposrednega lepljenja slike v tej aplikaciji.";
"Copy any text, then tap the 'Add from Clipboard' button in the Cutling keyboard to save it as a new cutling" = "Kopirajte katero koli besedilo, nato tapnite gumb „Dodaj iz odložišča“ na Cutling tipkovnici, da ga shranite kot nov cutling";
"You can manage all your cutlings in the main Cutling app. Changes you make will instantly appear in your keyboard." = "Vse svoje cutlinge lahko upravljate v glavni aplikaciji Cutling. Spremembe, ki jih naredite, se bodo takoj pojavile na vaši tipkovnici.";
"Keyboard extensions have strict memory limits to ensure system stability. Images use more memory than text, so we limit them to ensure your keyboard stays fast and reliable. If you reach a limit, simply delete some cutlings to add new ones." = "Razširitve tipkovnice imajo stroge omejitve pomnilnika za zagotavljanje stabilnosti sistema. Slike porabijo več pomnilnika kot besedilo, zato jih omejujemo, da vaša tipkovnica ostane hitra in zanesljiva. Če dosežete omejitev, preprosto izbrišite nekaj cutlingov, da dodate nove.";
